class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Application\\Handler\\StepDispatcher"
type: readonly final class
summary: The StepDispatcher class orchestrates the execution of agent steps by routing effects and messages to distinct message buses. It decouples side-effect processing from publishing logic by delegating to separate MessageBusInterface instances.
effects: dispatches messages to executionBus and publisherBus
dependencies: "MessageBusInterface $executionBus, MessageBusInterface $publisherBus"
